Sunn Mere Dil Episode 26 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by LUX - Happilac Paints and Ujooba Beauty Cream - Wahaj Ali - Maya Ali - 1st January 2025 - Har Pal Geo

Sunn Mera Dil Digitally Presented by LUX - Happilac Paints and Ujooba Beauty Cream

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated mega signature project, Sunn Mere Dil, is the most awaited drama serial. The mega drama boasts a star-studded cast led by Wahaj Ali and Maya Ali. Written by the renowned Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar and directed by the acclaimed Haseeb Hasan, Sunn Mere Dil promises to be a one-of-a-kind drama.

Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person’s devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about
possession but about selflessness.

Every unspoken gesture and unseen act of kindness brings them fulfillment, as they put their beloved’s happiness above their own, showing that love is not just about being together, it’s about redefining happiness, even at the expense of their contentment.

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Haseeb Hasan
Writer: Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar

Cast:

snippet.title: Walmik Karad अखेर पुण्यात सरेंडर, कराडसाठी आलेले कार्यकर्ते का पळत होते? CID | Santosh Deshmukh
snippet.description:
#MumbaiTakNews  #LatestMarathiNews #MaharashtraPolitics

वाल्मिक कराड यांच्यावर सध्या राज्याचं लक्ष लागून असतानाच आता वाल्मिक कराड आता शरण आला आहे. याप्रकरणातली ही आतापर्यंतची सर्वात मोठी अपडेट असून, यापुढे होणाऱ्या सर्व कारवाईवर आता राज्याचं लक्ष असणार आहे. वाल्मिक कराड यांनी एक व्हिडीओ शेअर करत यावरुन आपली भूमिका स्पष्ट केली आहे. त्यानंतर पुण्यातील पाषाण येथील CID कार्यालयात तो शरण आला आहे.

🔴लॉग इन करा: https://www.mumbaitak.in/
Follow us on :
Google News : https://news.google.com/publications/CAAqBwgKMLeLpAsw-pW8Aw?hl=mr&gl=IN&ceid=IN%3Amr
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/mumbaitak
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/mumbaitak
Twitter: https://twitter.com/mumbai_tak
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLzHYo6L3SZJGBWc_BPfqMt5Yq24d_AXCa

#maharashtra #marathi #marathinews

इंडिया टुडेच्या मुंबई तक या मराठी युट्यूब चॅनलवर आपलं स्वागत. इंडिया टुडे ग्रुपचे मॅगझिन, इंडिया टुडे टीव्ही आणि आज तक हे लोकप्रिय न्यूज चॅनल आपल्याला माहितीच आहे. त्यानंतर आता खास मराठी प्रेक्षकांसाठी आपण भारतीय प्रादेशिक भाषेतलं पहिलं मराठी चॅनल घेऊन आलोय. महाराष्ट्रासह राष्ट्रीय आणि आंतरराष्ट्रीयस्तरावरील महत्वाच्या बातम्या आणि घडामोडी आपल्याला अगदी सोप्या शब्दांत समजावण्याचा आमचा प्रयत्न असणार आहे. 
Namskar, Welcome to India Today group’s new Marathi YouTube channel – Mumbai Tak. Get all the latest important stories and updates from in and around Maharashtra in Marathi. Stay Tuned to Mumbai Tak for current affairs, politics, sports, business, entertainment, literature and many more in Marathi.

snippet.title: CHICKEN 65 IDLI | Fried Chicken Idli Recipe Cooking In Village | Idli Cooking with Chicken Recipe
snippet.description:
n this video, we bring you a unique and mouthwatering recipe, Chicken 65 Idli!  A fusion of South Indian tradition and spicy flavors, this dish combines soft, fluffy idlis with crispy, flavorful fried chicken. Watch as we prepare this innovative recipe in our beautiful village setting, using fresh ingredients and traditional cooking methods.

What’s special about this recipe?

The perfect blend of soft idlis and spicy Chicken 65.
Simple steps that you can follow to recreate this dish at home.
A wholesome and flavorful meal for all occasions!
Join us for this delicious adventure filled with authentic village vibes.

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. snippet.description:
#currentaffairs2024 #currentaffairsrevision #kumargauravsir 

“सपने उनके सच होते हैं, जिनके हौसलों में जान होती है।”  
इसी विश्वास के साथ #Kumar_Gaurav_Sir  द्वारा हर सुबह 6:30 बजे #Daily_Current_Affairs की बेहतरीन #Class ली जा रही है।  

आज की इस Maha Revision Class में सर आपके लिए लेकर आए हैं 1 January 2024 से 31 December 2024 तक के सभी महत्वपूर्ण करेंट अफेयर्स का संपूर्ण महा Revision, जो आपकी आगामी सभी Competitive Exams के लिए एक मजबूत आधार बनेगा। यह क्लास आपके सरकारी नौकरी के सपने को सच करने में एक अहम भूमिका निभा सकती है।

snippet.title: Sudhma Andhare Exclusive: वाल्मिक कराड सरेंडर होताच धडाधड नावं घेत अंधारेंचे गौप्यस्फोट
snippet.description:
#MumbaiTakNews  #LatestMarathiNews #MaharashtraPolitics
Sudhma Andhare Exclusive: वाल्मिक कराड सरेंडर होताच धडाधड नावं घेत अंधारेंचे गौप्यस्फोट... वाल्मिक कराड यांच्यावर सध्या राज्याचं लक्ष लागून असतानाच आता वाल्मिक कराड आता शरण आला आहे. याप्रकरणातली ही आतापर्यंतची सर्वात मोठी अपडेट असून, यापुढे होणाऱ्या सर्व कारवाईवर आता राज्याचं लक्ष असणार आहे. वाल्मिक कराड यांनी एक व्हिडीओ शेअर करत यावरुन आपली भूमिका स्पष्ट केली आहे. त्यानंतर पुण्यातील पाषाण येथील CID कार्यालयात तो शरण आला आहे.



🔴लॉग इन करा: https://www.mumbaitak.in/
Follow us on :
Google News : https://news.google.com/publications/CAAqBwgKMLeLpAsw-pW8Aw?hl=mr&gl=IN&ceid=IN%3Amr
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/mumbaitak
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/mumbaitak
Twitter: https://twitter.com/mumbai_tak
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLzHYo6L3SZJGBWc_BPfqMt5Yq24d_AXCa

#maharashtra #marathi #marathinews

इंडिया टुडेच्या मुंबई तक या मराठी युट्यूब चॅनलवर आपलं स्वागत. इंडिया टुडे ग्रुपचे मॅगझिन, इंडिया टुडे टीव्ही आणि आज तक हे लोकप्रिय न्यूज चॅनल आपल्याला माहितीच आहे. त्यानंतर आता खास मराठी प्रेक्षकांसाठी आपण भारतीय प्रादेशिक भाषेतलं पहिलं मराठी चॅनल घेऊन आलोय. महाराष्ट्रासह राष्ट्रीय आणि आंतरराष्ट्रीयस्तरावरील महत्वाच्या बातम्या आणि घडामोडी आपल्याला अगदी सोप्या शब्दांत समजावण्याचा आमचा प्रयत्न असणार आहे.

mr.title: Sudhma Andhare Exclusive: वाल्मिक कराड सरेंडर होताच धडाधड नावं घेत अंधारेंचे गौप्यस्फोट
mr.description:
#MumbaiTakNews  #LatestMarathiNews #MaharashtraPolitics
Sudhma Andhare Exclusive: वाल्मिक कराड सरेंडर होताच धडाधड नावं घेत अंधारेंचे गौप्यस्फोट... वाल्मिक कराड यांच्यावर सध्या राज्याचं लक्ष लागून असतानाच आता वाल्मिक कराड आता शरण आला आहे. याप्रकरणातली ही आतापर्यंतची सर्वात मोठी अपडेट असून, यापुढे होणाऱ्या सर्व कारवाईवर आता राज्याचं लक्ष असणार आहे. वाल्मिक कराड यांनी एक व्हिडीओ शेअर करत यावरुन आपली भूमिका स्पष्ट केली आहे. त्यानंतर पुण्यातील पाषाण येथील CID कार्यालयात तो शरण आला आहे.

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: INDIA'S GOT LATENT Bouncer Breaks Character | Dostcast w/ Amin Khan
snippet.description:
Amin Khan is a professional bodyguard and has been a bouncer for 18 years in Mumbai. He was a Maharashtra-level bodybuilder and has provided security to celebrities like Poonam Pandey and Nora Fatehi. He has also acted in movies like Ready with Salman Khan. Currently, he is a bouncer on Samay Raina’s show India’s Got Latent.

In this episode, Vinamre and Amin talk about:

•His early days during his bodybuilding career and the consumption of steroids
•The craziest experiences of being a bouncer, Handling crowds in high-pressure situations
•The process of securing VIPs in different scenarios, How celebrities are in real life
•His experience working with Salman Khan in a movie and Amitabh Bachchan in KBC
•The struggles and challenges faced by bouncers, His experiences in dance bars and clubs

Watch this episode to uncover the real-life story of Andrew Tate of India’s Got Latent.

Timestamps:

00:00 - Introduction
0:50 - Who is Amin Khan?
4:40 - Craziest 'India's Got Latent' episode
7:02 - Why are bouncers rude?
7:58 - Craziest experience of being a bouncer
15:45 - Dangerous club experience
20:30 - Dance bar culture in Mumbai
22:10 - How much does a bouncer earn?
25:17 - Working with Salman Khan and Amitabh Bachchan
28:10 - His life after 'India's Got Talent'
30:00 - Reality of celebrities
36:00 - Samay Raina in real life
38:48 - Problems faced by bouncers
41:08 - Salman Khan and Jackie Shroff in real life
43:07 - Drugs and stag entry in clubs
47:55 - Conclusion

en-IN.title: INDIA'S GOT LATENT Bouncer Breaks Character | Dostcast w/ Amin Khan
en-IN.description:
Amin Khan is a professional bodyguard and has been a bouncer for 18 years in Mumbai. He was a Maharashtra-level bodybuilder and has provided security to celebrities like Poonam Pandey and Nora Fatehi. He has also acted in movies like Ready with Salman Khan. Currently, he is a bouncer on Samay Raina’s show India’s Got Latent.

In this episode, Vinamre and Amin talk about:

•His early days during his bodybuilding career and the consumption of steroids
•The craziest experiences of being a bouncer, Handling crowds in high-pressure situations
•The process of securing VIPs in different scenarios, How celebrities are in real life
•His experience working with Salman Khan in a movie and Amitabh Bachchan in KBC
•The struggles and challenges faced by bouncers, His experiences in dance bars and clubs

Watch this episode to uncover the real-life story of Andrew Tate of India’s Got Latent.

snippet.title: क्यों खास है SpaDex Mission जिसे ISRO ने किया Launch, देखिए ये रिपोर्ट
snippet.description:
ISRO यानी इंडियन स्पेस रिसर्च ऑर्गेनाइजेशन अंतरिक्ष में इतिहास रचने जा रहा है. दरअसल ISRO स्पेडेक्स मिशन को लॉन्च कर रहा है. स्पेडेक्स मिशन के तहत अंतरिक्ष में ट्रैवल कर रहे दो स्पेसक्राफ्ट को आपस में जोड़ा जाएगा. इस प्रक्रिया को डॉकिंग कहा जाता है. जो बहुत जटिल है. लेकिन, अगर ISRO को अपने मिशन में सफलता मिलती है. तो अमेरिका, रूस और चीन के बाद ऐसा करने वाला दुनिया का चौथा देश बन जाएगा भारत.

ISRO यानी इंडियन स्पेस रिसर्च ऑर्गेनाइजेशन अंतरिक्ष में इतिहास रचने जा रहा है. दरअसल ISRO स्पेडेक्स मिशन को लॉन्च कर रहा है. स्पेडेक्स मिशन के तहत अंतरिक्ष में ट्रैवल कर रहे दो स्पेसक्राफ्ट को आपस में जोड़ा जाएगा. इस प्रक्रिया को डॉकिंग कहा जाता है. जो बहुत जटिल है. लेकिन, अगर ISRO को अपने मिशन में सफलता मिलती है. तो अमेरिका, रूस और चीन के बाद ऐसा करने वाला दुनिया का चौथा देश बन जाएगा भारत.
#SpadexMission #ISRO #Science
Video Courtsey-ISRO

snippet.description:
In the 1st T20I, Sri Lanka and New Zealand went head-to-head at the Bay Oval. Sri Lanka won the toss and asked the home team to bat first. The Kiwis posted 172 runs on the board for 8 wickets in their 20 overs. Sri Lanka started their innings strongly with Nissanka scoring 90 runs. At last the Kiwis won the match by 8 runs.

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

વિક્સ ની ગોળીયો તમે ખીસા માં રાખજો
હો બેનપણીયો ભાળી દોડ બહુ કરોશો
ઓઠે ઓઠે જઈ તમે મને તાકોશો

જાનુ મારા દિલ નો પતંગ જો

snippet.title: Suvendu Adhikari: রাস্তার দুধারে সমর্থকদের ভিড়, হাত নেড়ে অভ্যর্থনা শুভেন্দুকে
snippet.description:
ABP Ananda LIVE : পুলিশের অনুমতি না থাকা সত্ত্বেও সভা হচ্ছে সন্দেশখালিতে। রাস্তার দুধারে সমর্থকদের ভিড়, হাত নেড়ে অভ্যর্থনা শুভেন্দুকে। আজ সন্দেশখালিতে শুভেন্দু অধিকারীর সভা, অনুমতি দিল না পুলিশ। সভার জন্য আগেই সন্দেশখালি থানায় আবেদন জানিয়েছিল বিজেপি। যে মাঠে সভা হওয়ার কথা, তা সরকারি জমি। সরকারি জমিতে সভা করতে গেলে সম্মতিপত্র লাগে, সেই সম্মতিপত্র সময়মতো দেওয়া হয়নি। কত লোক সভায় আসতে পারেন, সে বিষয়ে কিছু জানানো হয়নি, তাই সভার জন্য লিখিত অনুমতি দেওয়া হয়নি, জানাল পুলিশ।

snippet.title: MELBOURNE REPORT,VIKRANT GUPTA: SORRY NITISH BAHUBALI🙏BUT क्या दिग्गज BATSMEN आपसे सीखेंगे? INDvsAUS
snippet.description:
VIKRANT GUPTA, DAY 3 REPORT: India's rising star Nitish Reddy hit a brilliant hundred and was beautifully complemented by Washington Sundar's rearguard as India reached 358 for 9 before rain forced early stumps on Day 3 of the Boxing Day Test at the Melbourne Cricket Ground. Nitish and Sundar added 127 runs for the eighth wicket to cut India's deficit to 116 after Australia's 474 in Melbourne.
Day 3 was Test cricket at its raw and pulsating best, a reminder of why the Australia-India rivalry stands at the pinnacle of the format. Reddy and Sundar fought back, but Australia remained in a strong position, poised to secure a significant first-innings lead.
